        "ggOkzpODfF8_text": "I Have to be Honest, I was 100% Sure this Viral Korean Collagen Mask I saw on Social Media was Just a Scam…",
        "ggMTtLiPXuX_text": "<p><i>By Cerissa Stevens | September 2025</i></p>",
        "ggVAXwM1zAm_text": "<p>Hey, I’m Cerissa — a mom of two and a busy project manager.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Between school runs and deadlines, I barely get five minutes to myself.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Looking in the mirror was tough: <strong>deep lines, uneven texture, and a tired face</strong> that expensive creams couldn’t fix.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I just missed the healthy, glowing skin I used to have — <strong>until I came across this video…</strong></p>",
        "ggK_H0sNv4M_text": "The Discovery:",
        "ggLAZivUiEX_text": "<p>One evening, while scrolling through Instagram after a long day, a video caught my eye.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It was a woman, around my age, wearing a mask. At first it looked like a milky white sheet — but after a few hours, it turned completely clear as <strong>her skin absorbed it.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Her ‘after’ shot was stunning. <strong>Plump, dewy, glass-like skin. It was the Nifora Bio-Collagen Mask.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>My first thought? <i><strong>It could be just another gimmick.</strong></i><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>But I couldn’t stop thinking about her glow. And when I saw the comments filled with women raving about their own results, I thought: <i><strong>what have I got to lose?</strong></i><strong>”</strong></p>",
        "ggl0ibjLGim_text": "The First Experience:",
        "ggZEa3ntaM6_text": "<p>When the masks arrived, I decided to try one that very night.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The mask itself felt cool and substantial, soaked, but not drippy.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It molded to my face perfectly, like a second skin. And it actually stayed put—no slipping and sliding around like those cheap paper ones.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>So, I put on a movie and let it work its magic.</p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_585371332628185746": {
      "type": "gp-section-585371332628185746",
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "d3109d5fc083d0d1d0309fce918ffd40311c102a935219d44d0c37e35b838373_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggheHoiT6v9_text": "<p>After 30 minutes</p>",
        "ggJp78p-XaN_text": "<p>I peeked in the mirror. Just like in the video, I could see some areas, especially around my cheeks and forehead, starting to turn transparent.</p>",
        "ggmn3lJahwb_text": "<p>After 30 minutes</p>",
        "ggQ4ReC5Ae5_text": "<p>After an hour</p>",
        "ggO1t8JFm2C_text": "<p>My skin felt tighter in a good way. It felt like all those ingredients was being shrink-wrapped into my face.</p>",
        "ggzd2CzW5yf_text": "<p>After an hour</p>",
        "ggtOmdfRXgm_text": "<p>After 3-4 hours</p>",
        "ggU4ms-4W10_text": "<p>I looked in the mirror and was shocked. The mask was almost completely clear. All that amazing essence was now in my skin.</p>",
        "ggJ-Oe-NJmq_text": "<p>After 3-4 hours</p>"
      }
    },
    "gp_section_585372505322029714": {
      "type": "gp-section-585372505322029714",
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "0357afa6fae45746f2ba43d6bff87de85ae575253d2c9def3d8f684a1b6f7167_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggGr1fDUIvX_text": "<p><strong>The moment of truth.</strong> When I peeled it off, my face was plump, hydrated, and glowing.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The lines between my brows looked <strong>softer</strong>, and my whole face had a<strong> luminous, rested glow.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It was the kind of result <strong>I seriously thought</strong> you could only get from a professional facial.</p>",
        "ggaVSjomF8K_text": "The Transformation:",
        "ggA0r5ItbCb_text": "<p>I thought the glow would fade overnight — <strong>but it didn’t.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>My skin still felt <strong>incredibly hydrated and smooth.</strong> My makeup went on better than it had in years.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Now I use the Nifora mask twice a week, and the results are impressing!</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>My <strong>skin’s elasticity has improved</strong>, and the fine lines that used to bother me are far <strong>less noticeable.</strong></p>",
        "ggNyCLVZokv_text": "Why It Works:",
        "ggC11jYI1HG_text": "<p>I had to dig deeper (project manager brain, I can’t help it) — <strong>and suddenly it all made sense.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The Nifora mask isn’t just a sheet soaked in serum. <strong>It’s a</strong> <strong>hydrogel mask</strong>.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>This gel-like material locks in way more nutrients and seals them against your skin.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>As it warms up, it slowly melts, releasing the serum so <strong>your skin absorbs it</strong> much deeper.</p>",
        "gg9nESm6q8e_label": "<p>Try the Nifora Bio-Collagen Mask Today</p>",
        "ggfuSXdrGXq_text": "What really changed my mind?",
        "ggxN-W6-Kls_text": "<p>Look, I get it. The beauty world is full of empty promises.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>I was the BIGGEST skeptic.</strong> But seeing my own skin transform has been a game-changer for my confidence.&nbsp;</p><p><br>At 45, it’s about looking like the best, most rested version of myself.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>And this mask delivers: <strong>deep, lasting hydration</strong> — <strong>the foundation of youthful, healthy skin.</strong></p>",
        "ggrjuUHW3Al_text": "<p><strong>Stop wasting money on products that don't work.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>If you’re tired of seeing dull, dehydrated skin in the mirror — and want to finally wake up with that plump, hydrated <i>glass skin glow</i> — you need to try the <strong>Nifora Bio-Collagen Mask</strong>.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It’s been a <strong>true game-changer </strong>for me, and I honestly believe it can be for you too.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Don’t wait another day to feel this confident in your own skin.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>xx Cerissa</p>",
        "ggJw6IWuOwC_label": "<p>SHOP NOW</p>"
      }
